# Content is managed via Decap CMS (see apps/web/public/admin) and stored as
# Git-tracked files under apps/web/content/ — no database is required.
#
# Editor authentication is a GitHub OAuth App, brokered by the standalone
# Cloudflare Worker in workers/decap-oauth (no Netlify dependency). See
# apps/web/.env.example and workers/decap-oauth/.dev.vars.example for the
# actual variables, and docs/DEPLOYMENT.md for full setup instructions.
